metadata.name: Gods & Titans - Royalty NFT #1
metadata.description: When you mint a Gods & Titans NFT you will also receive a FREE Royalty NFT. This Royalty NFT is like a receipt to show you are the owner of an original minted Gods & Titans NFT, it also holds access to all the holder rewards you are entitled to. As new products are launched, new rewards can be added to this Royalty NFT.
